  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This randomized, open-label study is aimed to evaluate the efficacy of high-dose icotinib in
      treating advanced non-small cell lung cancer patients with positive EGFR 21 exon mutation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
